  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>You must beat down the masses to have true order.</em><br /><br /><strong>Prerequisites</strong><br />10 Hit Dice, lawful evil alignment.<br /><br /><strong>Benefits</strong><br />You can store a number of affirmations up to your Charisma bonus (minimum 1) to use at any time, not just within the next 24 hours. You can use an affirmation to cast hold person as a spell-like ability as a standard action, with a caster level equal to your Hit Dice. You gain a +2 bonus on weapon and spell damage rolls against chaotic and good creatures (or +4 if the creature is both chaotic and good). This is an alignment-based effect.</p>\n<p><br /><strong>Residual</strong><br />If you have this feat but you are no longer lawful evil, you continue to gain the +2 bonus on weapon and spell damage rolls against chaotic and good creatures (or a +4 bonus if the creature is both chaotic and good).</p>",
